    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/b7acad6e34f7b7ee1d69ba34a8e5ddff.poster.avif?t=1770802543\" width=720 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/b7acad6e34f7b7ee1d69ba34a8e5ddff.webm?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/b7acad6e34f7b7ee1d69ba34a8e5ddff.mp4?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《破晶者》是一款快节奏弹幕双摇杆动作类肉鸽游戏，让您亲手打造专属魔法。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破晶者们粉碎了万物之源“初光”，窃取散落的晶片来强化自身、稳固统治。踏入黑暗深渊，创造毁灭魔法，夺回曾经维系世界的原初力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/c460724fdd4d296cdf6d2f83307b545b.avif?t=1770802543\" width=1438 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身迅捷的猎人、睿智的法师，或坚韧的骑士——每位英雄都拥有独特鲜明的战斗风格，足以激发您的策略潜能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着破晶者不断进化，更多英雄将从混乱中崛起，带来无尽的冒险可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/ed28936bafe6ec18bdb0af23323aacec.poster.avif?t=1770802543\" width=740 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/ed28936bafe6ec18bdb0af23323aacec.webm?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/ed28936bafe6ec18bdb0af23323aacec.mp4?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/15433a8beee9662ad5811ac6850a55f0.avif?t=1770802543\" width=1438 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备迎接无间断的高速战斗吧，每一秒都至关重要。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特设计的敌人拥有各不相同的移动方式、攻击模式与战术定位。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在匠心构筑的生态环境中奋战，让环境威胁与敌人组合不断打磨您的技艺，将您逼至极限。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有冗余内容，没有喘息机会——唯有战斗、闪避与突破。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/2b66f46c80d7a15b1cc0879d466ce778.poster.avif?t=1770802543\" width=740 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/2b66f46c80d7a15b1cc0879d466ce778.webm?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/2b66f46c80d7a15b1cc0879d466ce778.mp4?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/a9e97500d12c90039d13ad3c963789fc.avif?t=1770802543\" width=1438 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夺回并组合晶片，打造足以毁灭一切的魔法。越深入黑暗，您的魔法力量便越混乱，也更具创造性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/cbe6dc48c29e4c4c4def4b7371fcb0be.poster.avif?t=1770802543\" width=740 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/cbe6dc48c29e4c4c4def4b7371fcb0be.webm?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/cbe6dc48c29e4c4c4def4b7371fcb0be.mp4?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/569f6006b236d50a01e9c68a95211749.avif?t=1770802543\" width=1438 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险使用过程生成技术，带来全新的敌人、战利品与构筑选择。解锁新英雄、拓展技能树、获得永久升级，在每一次归来后都变得更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/0ac7061766a89649ca95552effc010b7.poster.avif?t=1770802543\" width=740 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/0ac7061766a89649ca95552effc010b7.webm?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3256040/extras/0ac7061766a89649ca95552effc010b7.mp4?t=1770802543\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>您的反馈至关重要</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的反馈对我们意义重大。我们期待倾听您的想法，并以此不断打磨《破晶者》。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >立即将《破晶者》添加至愿望单，与我们一同见证并参与游戏的持续开发历程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
